Use of perfmon
1.	Type perfmon or performance monitor on the vm
 
2.	On the board where you see the red line, right click and click “Add Counter”
 
3.	Add counter from the lists e.g. "logic disk" and select/deselect from the lists of counters. Then click “add” and “OK”
 
NB: Lists are alphabetical

For Azure DISK IO
